#

Turkey Lettuce Wraps with Hoisin Sauce

25 min
$12.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick Meal

Description

Fresh and crunchy turkey wraps with a sweet and savory hoisin sauce.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 lb
  • lettuce leaves (iceberg or butter): 8 leaves
  • hoisin sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • green onions, chopped: 2
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • ginger, grated: 1 teaspoon
  • carrots, shredded: 1/2 cup
  • soy sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
